This directory contains interface programs to generate html pages from the CSV files Cantowise. Sample files for Canto-1 are included.

A) To generate html interface for the shlokas in a given Canto

Usage: SCLINSTALLDIR/SHMT/prog/reader_generator/interface_gen.sh $1 $2 $3
where
$1 ->  src_dir_path
$2 ->  total shlokas
$3 ->  target

For example, to generate an interface for the 10 shlokas in the Canto-I in the target directory SV-I
run it as
	SCLINSTALLDIR/SHMT/prog/reader_generator/interface_gen.sh Canto-I 10 SV-1

B) To change the names of rows in Hide/Show
   make changes in SCLINSTALLDIR/SHMT/prog/reader_generator/style_script/text.js

C) To change the color scheme:
   make changes in SCLINSTALLDIR/SHMT/prog/reader_generator/style_script/style.css
D) To control the initial display of rows
   make changes in SCLINSTALLDIR/SHMT/prog/reader_generator/style_script/text.js and SCLINSTALLDIR/SHMT/prog/reader_generator/style_script/text.css
  1 in text.js stands for disply the row, and 0 not to display the row
  none in text.css stands for not to display the row.
  The entries in text.js and text.css should match.

